## Debt Management

### Review Schedule
- Review weekly during planning phase
- Prioritize based on impact
- Track resolution progress
- Document learnings

### Resolution Process
1. Identify debt during review phase
2. Prioritize based on impact
3. Plan resolution in next cycle
4. Execute resolution
5. Document resolution

